This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Include all codes defined in http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/CodeSystem/match-confidence-level
  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/match-grade

name: MatchConfidenceLevelValueSet
title: Match Confidence Level Code System
description: Codes indicating confidence level of matched entities
